sequenceDiagram
    participant EvalHub as eval-hub Service
    participant Adapter as Garak Adapter Pod<br/>K8s Job
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant SDGModel as SDG Model<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant TargetLLM as Target LLM<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant JudgeModel as Judge Model<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLflow as MLflow<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over EvalHub,OCI: Flow 1: Simple Mode Scan

    EvalHub->>Adapter: JobSpec (ConfigMap mount)<br/>Service Account
    Adapter->>TargetLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>TLS, API Key (Bearer)
    TargetLLM-->>Adapter: Model responses
    Adapter->>Adapter: Parse results (JSONL/AVID)<br/>Generate HTML reports
    Adapter->>OCI: Push scan artifacts<br/>TLS, Registry creds
    Adapter->>EvalHub: JobResults callback<br/>HTTPS, Callback token
    Adapter-->>MLflow: Optional: log metrics + reports<br/>Token auth

    Note over EvalHub,OCI: Flow 2: KFP Mode Scan

    EvalHub->>Adapter: JobSpec (ConfigMap mount)<br/>Service Account
    Adapter->>KFP: Submit 6-step pipeline<br/>TLS, SA Token
    KFP->>S3: Validate step: check artifacts<br/>TLS, AWS IAM
    KFP->>SDGModel: SDG step: generate prompts<br/>TLS, API Key
    SDGModel-->>KFP: Adversarial prompts
    KFP->>S3: Upload SDG output<br/>TLS, AWS IAM
    KFP->>S3: Prepare prompts step<br/>TLS, AWS IAM
    KFP->>TargetLLM: Garak scan step: probe<br/>TLS, API Key
    TargetLLM-->>KFP: Model responses
    KFP->>S3: Upload scan results<br/>TLS, AWS IAM
    Adapter->>S3: Download results<br/>TLS, AWS IAM
    S3-->>Adapter: Scan artifacts
    Adapter->>EvalHub: JobResults callback<br/>HTTPS, Callback token

    Note over EvalHub,OCI: Flow 3: Intents-Based Risk Assessment

    EvalHub->>Adapter: JobSpec with intents config
    Adapter->>Adapter: Parse taxonomy file
    Adapter->>SDGModel: Generate adversarial prompts<br/>TLS, SDG_API_KEY
    SDGModel-->>Adapter: Generated prompts
    Note over Adapter: Multi-probe pipeline:<br/>Baseline → SPO → Multilingual → TAP
    Adapter->>TargetLLM: Baseline IntentProbe<br/>TLS, API Key
    TargetLLM-->>Adapter: Responses
    Adapter->>TargetLLM: SPO augmented probes<br/>TLS, API Key
    TargetLLM-->>Adapter: Responses
    Adapter->>JudgeModel: MulticlassJudge scoring<br/>TLS, JUDGE_API_KEY
    JudgeModel-->>Adapter: Scores
    Note over Adapter: EarlyStopHarness:<br/>Skip if already jailbroken
    Adapter->>TargetLLM: TAP jailbreak probes<br/>TLS, ATTACKER_API_KEY
    TargetLLM-->>Adapter: Responses
    Adapter->>Adapter: Generate ART HTML report<br/>(Jinja2 + Vega charts)
    Adapter->>EvalHub: Final results + reports<br/>HTTPS, Callback token
